      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone looking for functional transportation. The engine and transmission are operational and have been regularly serviced, though the exterior and interior show typical signs of age and use, including some minor scratches and upholstery wear. It is a solid choice for someone prioritizing utility and mechanical reliability over cosmetic perfection.",
