    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-grade example that defies its age. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, retaining its original factory luster with zero paint corrections or touch-ups. The exterior is flawless, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating, while the interior remains in a showroom-fresh state\u2014no wear on the bolsters, no creasing in the leather, and still carrying that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach; every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with a comprehensive binder of records included. The engine bay is pristine, and the undercarriage shows no signs of road debris or weathering. This sale includes both original keys, the factory window sticker, and all original manuals. For the discerning collector who demands perfection, this is an investment-grade opportunity.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
